# MLIR: call @std.bigint.modInverse
# MLIR-LABEL: func.func @addPoints
# MLIR: call @std.bigint.modInverse
# MLIR-LABEL: func.func @scalarMultiplyStep
# MLIR: bigint.and
# MLIR: bigint.shift_right
# MLIR: call @addPoints
# MLIR: call @doublePoint

